name: CarryAll Convertible Tote
description:
The CarryAll is a durable Tote Bag, which easily converts to a Messenger Bag, or a Briefcase, WITH NO EXTRA STRAPS or hardware. The CarryAll is a high quality tote that comfortably holds everything you need for the day, and has easily convertible handles to help you take on any situation you might encounter along the way. It will gladly be the professional Briefcase for a day at the office, the Shoulder Bag that works best for grocery shopping, and the Messenger Bag you want for the ride home. The CarryAll is handmade from high-quality waterproof polyester & hand-waxed leather, which means itâ€™ll be around for the long haul, and will keep getting more beautiful with age. You can check out the Kickstarter Video below for more info....Thanks!

CarryAll Convertible Tote from Blank Brand on Vimeo.

name: Shoulder Pack Messenger Bag / White
description:
The Shoulder Pack is a beautifully simple bag that will happily carry whatever you need - it works great when heading to the office, running to the grocery store, or hopping on a plane. It will quickly adjust & adapt to your needs and your life. The Shoulder Pack has a clean look, with pockets inside and along the top edge, and also a series of interchangeable sleeves that can handle just about any tablet or laptop you want to bring with you. The bag itself is made from a high quality waterproof vinyl, which is durable and easy to keep clean. Also, the wide shoulder strap - made from soft nylon webbing with a natural leather pad - makes the bag comfortable to wear, no matter what you put inside. All of the materials for the Shoulder Pack come from the US, and every bag is handmade in Portland, Oregon, USA. To see a little more about the Shoulder Pack, and how Blank started, please check out this video:

Blank Brand Story from Blank Brand on Vimeo.

To see more about the Shoulder Pack, take a look at the video below:

The Shoulder Pack Bag: A Look Inside from Blank Brand on Vimeo.

---- If you would like a laptop or tablet Sleeve with your Shoulder Pack, the available sizes are: - Large Laptop (15in Macbook) - Small Laptop (13in Macbook) - Large Tablet (Ipad, Samsung 10.1) - Small Tablet (Ipad Mini, Google Nexus 7) (Just tell us in the notes which size sleeve you would like)

name: Simple Wallet / Leather
description:
The Simple Wallet is just that, a beautifully simple & thin wallet that will love holding your essentials. It has a pocket on each side, which are great for holding credit cards, cash, business cards, and tiny love notes. The Simple Wallet is made of vegetable tanned leather, that has been hand-treated with a natural wax finish. It will last a long time, and only get better looking with age. All materials for the Simple Wallet come from the US, and every wallet is handmade in Portland, Oregon, USA. To see the Simple Wallet in action (and the Sleeves, too), check out this video:

Blank Brand: Sleeves & Wallet from Blank Brand on Vimeo.

name: Folded Felt Laptop Sleeve / White
description:
This beautiful & minimal Sleeve will hold your device snugly (and help to protect against damage). The leather & industrial felt construction allows the Sleeve to wear very well (and actually look better over time), while being easy to use and get your device in & out. The Sleeves work well on their own, or as part of an interchangeable system with our Shoulder Pack Bag. Sizes are: - Large Laptop (15in Macbook) - Small Laptop (13in Macbook) And to see a bit more about the Sleeves (and the Simple Wallet, too), check out this video:

Blank Brand: Sleeves & Wallet from Blank Brand on Vimeo.
